    public static enum Slot.IdType
extends java.lang.Enum<Slot.IdType>
    An enum to define the identifier types of a slot. Five types is defined, which are "PRIVATEIP, PUBLICIP, VMID, VMHOSTNAME,NOTDEFINED ".
